## Basic Example

``hello.py``:

```python
import click

@click.command()
@click.argument('name')
def main(name):
    print('hello, {}!'.format(name))

main()
```


---

Terminal:

```bash
$ python hello.py --help
Usage: hello.py [OPTIONS] NAME

Options:
  --help  Show this message and exit.

$ python hello.py Bob
Hello, Bob!
```


