## Adding an Option

```python
import click

@click.command()
@click.argument('name')
@click.option('--reverse', is_flag=True)
def main(name, reverse):
    if reverse:
        name = name[::-1]
    print('hello, {}!'.format(name))

main()
```

Terminal:

```bash
$ python hello.py
```


